ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: No, the class was forced to cater to too broad a field of specializations to be effective. Discussion was also given to postmodern drivel, which tended to wallow in obscurity without seeking (and at times seemed to abhor) actual solutions to problems in interpreting commentary.
Lots or reading, lots of theory, but the material is so foundational and applicable to many topics within our field.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course did not contribute to my dissertation research at all.
